{
  "stem": "3474.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was so cold.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the deep-- the snow was very deep over there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We were marching over there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I still had my shoes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I still had my shoes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No socks, because they didn't give you no socks or underwear.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Just that thin striped uniform with a cap.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's all.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Just like pajamas.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Thin like pajamas.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Nothing-- it was-- if you wear pajamas to bed, that's what it was.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Nothing else.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "No underwear, nothing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "People were dying.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were marching in that snow.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I remember when we were marching, we stopped in a hay barn for a while.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A barn, you know?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There they give us bread and some soup, old-- from all this time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And no water, because [INAUDIBLE] snow.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So for the drink, we drank some-- we had some snow.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We melted snow down.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were there overnight.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then we went to a train.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't remember how many people, because a lot-- some people didn't go in.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Matter-- by the time we got to that barn, a lot of people got killed because anybody who remained behind-- three feet-- they just shot them right there and there in the gutters.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They left them there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Three feet.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's no [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Whoever could not walk, they cut them-- they shot them right down there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was an SS behind them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Every three feet there was an SS.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were all [INAUDIBLE], but you couldn't do nothing because they had the machine guns.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So whoever remained three feet behind the lines, they put-- they put them down, give them a bullet in their head.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we-- they left them right there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we got there, so-- Did you have a partner?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Friend-- no such thing as partner.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
